      </li>
      <li class="one_third">
        <article><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-cogs"></i></a>
          <div class="ta-center">
          <%= image_tag("icons/specialized.png", alt: "Specialized")%>
          </div>
          <h6 class="heading ta-center">Specialized</h6>
          <p>The customized solutions we create are designed to be focused specifically on what your business needs. <a class="ta-toggle-near ta-cursor"> More&raquo;</a> <span class="ta-span-near" style="visibility: hidden;">We keep the design simple and the costs low, because you only pay for what you need. </span></p>
