  <div class="wrapper">
    <!-- How it works section -->
    <div class="ta-section-black">
      <div class="ta-section-header">Getting Started</div>
      <div class="ta-section-wrapper">
        <div class="ta-section-paragraph ta-margin-left">
          <%= image_tag("icons/submit.png", alt: "Secure", class: "ta-step-icon" )%>
          <p class="ta-section-paragraph-title">1. Submit Request </p>
          <p class="ta-section-paragraph-text">You can submit a request for a project <a href="mailto:support@timelessapps.com?subject=Project%20Request&body=Project%20Type%20%28Website%2C%20Web%20Application%2C%20Desktop%20Application%29%3A%0D%0A%0D%0AProject%20Description%3A%0D%0A">here</a>. We can also be contacted <a href="/contact" >here</a>. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="ta-section-paragraph ta-margin-left">
          <%= image_tag("icons/review.png", alt: "Secure", class: "ta-step-icon" )%>
          <p class="ta-section-paragraph-title">2. Review Request </p>
          <p class="ta-section-paragraph-text">We will review the request and reach out to you to confirm the details. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="ta-section-paragraph ta-margin-left">
          <%= image_tag("icons/work.png", alt: "Secure", class: "ta-step-icon" )%>
          <p class="ta-section-paragraph-title">3. Work on Project</p>
          <p class="ta-section-paragraph-text">Once in progress, you can check on the status of the project <a href="/projects">here</a>. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="ta-section-paragraph ta-margin-left">
          <%= image_tag("icons/deliver.png", alt: "Secure", class: "ta-step-icon" )%>
          <p class="ta-section-paragraph-title">4. Deliver Project</p>
          <p class="ta-section-paragraph-text">When completed, we will contact you and provide instructions on using the product. </p>
        </div>
        <span class="ta-stretch"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="wrapper row3">
    <div class="hoc container clear ta-fc-grey"> 
      <div class="center btmspace-50">
        <h3 class="font-x2 nospace">Check your progress</h3>
        <p class="nospace">We keep track of the progress of all of our projects. Simply enter your project ID and search to check the progress. </p>
      </div>
    <form action="<%= projects_path %>" class="ta-center ta-search-space" method="get">
